    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Synopsis</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Poofie Plays God is an open world Puzzle game where your goal is to escape/kill you know who before he or the others kill you; thing is the forest you just moved in suddenly loops around the edges and you can't just leave.<br>You only have your computer and a map, everything else to lift the curse holding it all together is up to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Poofie knows who you are and  he needs you. big brother is watching though, and it's his head or yours.<br><br><br>------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238180/extras/1f8a300f8f4e3ec470005ee927e60b05.avif?t=1744031389\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238180/extras_big/1f8a300f8f4e3ec470005ee927e60b05.avif?t=1744031389 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>WHAT YOU GET:</strong></i></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>FULLY EXPLORABLE</i><strong> 1.1km²</strong> wide map</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Rich story hidden throughout</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchasing inventory to survive</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4-5 Different Enemies. Depends on how you see it</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shotgun<u><i><strong></strong></i></u></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 Different endings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Extra content available on purchase</i></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shotgun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Horror (blood 😨😱😱)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238180/extras/c650243d6df009b21c9c6acaf069cf63.poster.avif?t=1744031389\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238180/extras/c650243d6df009b21c9c6acaf069cf63.webm?t=1744031389\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238180/extras/c650243d6df009b21c9c6acaf069cf63.mp4?t=1744031389\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>RELEASE DAY</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238180/extras/9c89910071964bb3fad69021f43068cd.avif?t=1744031389\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238180/extras_big/9c89910071964bb3fad69021f43068cd.avif?t=1744031389 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_strike\">Yeah so Steam has a policy where you can't change the release date if it's 2 weeks away, i had to change it to only show it's releasing february. internally it's &quot;releasing feb 13th&quot; but It's actually releasing </span><strong><i><span class=\"bb_strike\">March 07th (19:00 CET, 10:00 PST)  </span></i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >its out<strong><i><br>    </i></strong><strong><i></i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>ITS NOT OVER YET</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>There are planned updates for the game coming shortly after its release. These include:</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>More areas and other content for Singleplayer</i></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Multiplayer</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Level editor &amp; sharing</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>VR support? only if you really want it</i> <br><i> </i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i> <br> <br> <br> <br> <br> <br>This game is a passion project of mine i started way back in 2021, when i was just 12 years old. I hope it motivates you to make something like this of your own and if there's anything you hate about it, Please tell me; this is my first commercial project and theres no other good way for me to know what i ought to change.<br>  <br>anyway, have fun!</i></p></li></ul>",
